sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Pipeline
    participant HybridRetriever
    participant SemanticRetriever
    participant KeywordRetriever
    participant FusionStrategy
    participant RerankerStage
    participant FormatterStage

    Client->>Pipeline: Execute(ctx, query)

    Note over Pipeline: Retrieval Stage
    Pipeline->>HybridRetriever: Retrieve(ctx, query, opts)

    par Parallel Retrieval
        HybridRetriever->>SemanticRetriever: Retrieve(ctx, query, preOpts)
        Note over SemanticRetriever: Delegates to inner<br/>Retriever (vector DB)
        SemanticRetriever-->>HybridRetriever: semanticDocs

        HybridRetriever->>KeywordRetriever: Retrieve(ctx, query, preOpts)
        Note over KeywordRetriever: BM25 scoring<br/>IDF * TF for each term
        KeywordRetriever-->>HybridRetriever: keywordDocs
    end

    Note over HybridRetriever: Fusion Stage
    HybridRetriever->>FusionStrategy: Fuse(semanticDocs, keywordDocs)
    Note over FusionStrategy: RRF: score = sum(1/(k+rank))<br/>or Linear: weighted normalized scores
    FusionStrategy-->>HybridRetriever: fusedDocs

    Note over HybridRetriever: Apply MinScore filter<br/>Limit to TopK
    HybridRetriever-->>Pipeline: []Document

    Note over Pipeline: Reranking Stage
    Pipeline->>RerankerStage: Rerank(ctx, query, docs)
    Note over RerankerStage: MMR: balance relevance<br/>vs. diversity<br/>or Score: sort by score
    RerankerStage-->>Pipeline: rerankedDocs

    Note over Pipeline: Formatting Stage
    Pipeline->>FormatterStage: Format(ctx, docs)
    Note over FormatterStage: Custom output<br/>formatting
    FormatterStage-->>Pipeline: formattedOutput

    Pipeline-->>Client: Result{Documents, Output}
